channel.title: Little problem whats wrong?
channel.description:

item.description:
@Kidpaparoach wrote:

Way to make me feel mean >.<
C:\REPLACE with cache name from dropbox\Maps\mapC means you want to upload the cache to dropbox which will host the cache for you the same way a source is hosted of your computer. When you put it on dropbox it’ll give you a website link put it in your cachedownloader.java and compile and it’ll work.

The reason why your getting flamed is because it looks obvious to us but your new and you don’t know that your meant to read the command prompt but yeah thats the problem. Sorry for being rude:(.
